{"tid":774155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[只用18億人民幣!!] 騰訊深圳總部的7大看點！","createTime":"2018-08-10T06:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T06:50:09.000Z","uid":155883,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32f1f92f455e939df7c4c5f04338010038e7583e","tid":774155,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"騰訊位於深圳濱海的全球新總部大廈最近正式亮相了。總投資約 18 億元人民幣，佔地面積約 18650 平方米。<br />\n<br />\n身為中國科企龍頭的騰訊，總部除了應用不少新科技，更致力打造活力的工作環境，絕對是員工們的嚮往，企業中的典範。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n新總部大樓總建築面積達 34.9 萬平方米，分南北兩塔；其中南塔248米高，共50層，北塔194米高，共39層，最多可容納1萬名員工。<br />\n<br />\n南北塔被三個不同的工作生活空間連接在一起，包括 2 ~ 5 層的「文化連接層」，22 ~ 26 層的「健康連接層」，和 35 ~ 37 層「知識連接層」。<br />\n<br />\n以下是騰訊大樓中不可錯過的 7 個看點：<br />\n<br />\n用手機召喚的智能電梯<br />\n<br />\n電梯系統納入了大樓物聯網，讓員工提前在微信上預約電梯和到達樓層，再到指定的電梯門等待。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n仿如置身高級餐廳的浪漫食堂<br />\n<br />\n你有想過在公司飯堂沐浴在陽光下吃牛扒嗎？騰訊的員工就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n貼心周到的辦公區<br />\n<br />\n大樓考慮到氣候條件，自然採光和通風良好，牆體按照深圳日照規律設計，帶有遮陽系統。<br />\n<br />\n透過建立員工數據模型，整理出一套「辦公空間規劃標準」，包括員工辦公桌尺寸，會議室大小，通道的尺寸大小等細節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n多個特色會議室<br />\n這種視野的會議室，可能員工都要愛上開會了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n快捷的臉部辨識系統<br />\n大樓每個出入口均有臉部辨識系統，員工「對正」鏡頭即可進出工作間，毋須攜帶職員卡或輸入密碼，辨別速度最快達 0.1 秒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n舒適的工作休閒區<br />\n<br />\n午休時間可以隨意躺卧，小睡片刻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各式各樣的康體設施<br />\n<br />\n一口氣爬三層樓的攀岩牆 ，大樓最佳自拍景點之一。在 100 米高空中，還有一條貫穿兩棟大樓的 300 米長室內環形跑道。另外還有跑步機、動感單車、羽毛球場、桌球等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n騰訊深圳總部大樓，體現了騰訊心目中對未來空間的想像：一個垂直型生態社區綜合體，樂於包容所有，連接一切，在這裡的每一個人，都可以自由地工作，快樂地生活。3<br />\n<a href=\"http://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/21309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F21309&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=0ad56673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/21309</a>"},{"pid":"005e28e662a5c3ada70c7ccb31b7906bb3bde3f2","tid":774155,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"Photo係點解"},{"pid":"69a47537e063debcbfaa2202f514812695da45b9","tid":774155,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"咪又係抄 屌"},{"pid":"7bfd038981e3f83365652216412c3d0558595cb2","tid":774155,"uid":33643,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"Photo From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bab529118003bb921f86d3da614bd77a1557b9","tid":774155,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bfd038981e3f83365652216412c3d0558595cb2","tid":774155,"uid":33643,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"Photo From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\nPhoto From Internet<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm